# You are in the THG CRM repository

Root: `thg-crm` (deploy target for `crm.thehammittgroup.com`).

## Interaction map

- **Leads list and detail**: `src/app/admin/contacts/page.tsx`, `src/app/admin/contacts/[id]/page.tsx`
- **Mutations**: `src/app/actions/crm.ts` (prefer server actions + `revalidatePath`, not ad hoc fetch to nonexistent routes)
- **Pipeline / stage UI**: `ContactStatusSelect.tsx`, `ContactStageTableCell.tsx` (list row), `ContactHeroPipelineStrip.tsx` (hero); values: `src/lib/crm/pipeline.ts`
- **Hero / inquiry**: `ContactRecordHero.tsx`, `ContactSubmissionMessagePanel.tsx` (edit or clear submission message via `updateContactMessage` / `clearContactMessage` in `crm.ts`)
- **Data model**: `prisma/schema.prisma` (`CrmContact`, `CrmClient`, etc.)

The marketing site repo is separate (`thehammittgroup-website`). Sync from site forms uses integration routes under `src/app/api/integrations/`.
